
# Text Editor

* Support for spellcheck defined in each bundle for
     
     * Comments
     
## Plugins
	* (D)CVS
	
	
### Detonator

* Allow the user and projects to subscribe to signals
* FileSystem signals
    * Some signals should be intercepted, for example, when you delete
    a directory from the FileSystemPane, the SCM should be able to
    caputre it.
    
### Spell check

* Spellcheck comments
* Check through pep8 

